Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 在偷拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.61,0:02:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太安静了 反而睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.28,0:02:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用你的摄魂机…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个时间留住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪陪我?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得我把杯子都带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光注意些蘩文缛节
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是想轻松征战
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个过分的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我恶作剧的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管外面是下雨或下雪都把我关在家门外
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.06,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连吃晚饭的时候都不开门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.10,0:03:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 也算是替一直忙于工作的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格管教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 其实我知道一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以在不被人发现的状态下 从后面的窗户进去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还守着这个秘密 这话只跟你说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10加普就靠岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备下船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是把罗巴带来比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在赞巴尼号上是它自己做出的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎幺说呢 我在想见到他们时该用什么表情才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经很出色了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.69,0:04:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…刚才是在夸我?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你离别半年的故乡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是尖端岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.54,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是你?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从哪里打的电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…尖端岛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在姐姐在军队的宿舍里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.35,0:05:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我估计春也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我可以跟她联系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个电话之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 姐姐肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算在这里停泊三天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不用担心你的划艇了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别去惹宪兵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为北方政府的进犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.50,0:05:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛上的军方警戒变的更加严格了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不说我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不要到处乱跑比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我只是在思考
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娜琪亚美 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜托你办件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 二号目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辅助武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风向变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西南方向 顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修正 三号目标
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要对我这么温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.02,0:06:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分数不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过反应值偶尔会极其低下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会集中精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也认为多愁善感是年轻人的特权
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很担心寺岡古市的情况吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况在新兵中也很常见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一心想着出成果
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.54,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等放下心的时候 心情就会一落千丈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可别让我失望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹给你打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保准吓你一跳 超超超大新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 快说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…他回来了 回尖端岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.61,0:07:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉他姐姐在宿舍以后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说让我打电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我们家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 到演武广场去…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在那里谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之?。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指竹原明之吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严密警戒他自己的住宅 竹原龙藏的诊所
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及有可能与他接触的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西村春怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:07:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现实之种因孤独而心碎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.88,0:08:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 开始沉闷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.85,0:08:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 二 旁边一盆 没开花的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是休诊日吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.96,0:08:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪费了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那样…你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 请进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候应该说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我回来了” 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之回到岛上了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在大概去见龙藏医生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之的朋友来我们家告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感觉有些不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她的名字非常好听
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐总算到了 娜琪亚美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.58,0:10:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.58,0:10:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你认识她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拯救的那个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有石化 现在仍然活着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…你说过的吧 会让他平安的回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点把他带回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 姐姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小绿先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是姐姐你叫我来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话 快回家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想呆在明之的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之对我而言 永远都是无可替代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:10:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉 擅自把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你母亲了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想算是…不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.69,0:11:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 好歹把房间打扫一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么脏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这已经算是比较整洁的了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡 要喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是问这回你又在研究什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这座岛上也不怎么太平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那右臂 是校车爆炸时受的伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 类似吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 也没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是个有才能的“庸医” 你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着父母的事情只有初恋就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 看起来虽然挺那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是希洛克吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让你见个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我救了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能用一两句话就解释清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要她还留有一点思考能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请装做没看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能原谅这位卉孩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望我能这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.20,0:13:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄宿在你身上的希洛克想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.21,0:13:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在也只是在寻求答案的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是受到了指引
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉…大家都想成为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹原明之有可能已经潜伏在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里待机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现对象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即要求各配置点增援
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是竹原龙藏医生吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有一些有关令郎的问题要问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你也能喜欢我家的橘子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思打扰你休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我的腰就是不争气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 阿兵哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来急诊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风纱特制健康双层便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待您再次惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:14:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得明之回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最近她不知怎么回事 一直怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐她一直就只顾看着前面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能拜托的人只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你这一点还真像春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.09,0:15:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙真的一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 小绿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,军队里的事没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正已经被开除了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭时回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定时报告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未确认到对象回家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其母亲也未有异常举动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告确认
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒位置变更
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位置 对象就读的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水里有铁锈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.05,0:16:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.81,0:16:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…回答呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这孩子老是爱恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训斥他的时候倒是装出一副再也不犯了的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天却又想出别的什么鬼点子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只好把他关在门外禁止吃晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还对邻居们说 “只要发现他往家里钻 就揍他”什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从诊所后山潜入厨房的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:18:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为当我想“他差不多该求饶了吧”而准备放他进来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子在道歉的时候 脸上沾了好多饭粒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到厨房一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.27,0:18:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子的晚饭…居然少一半
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时已经消了气 非常惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是我的儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.72,0:18:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 喜欢恶作剧也要有个限度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我们为这孩子的行踪 忙得焦头烂额的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他却悄悄的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我给你打过电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看上去很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定过一阵子就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹这点 我是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是他母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.23,0:19:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉因为一些事情想见你却见不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发型很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.24,0:19:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么回来了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么又想来见我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好开心 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到你的话 我就必须向上面报告你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你来见我的话 我是按耐不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我又不想把你交给军方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不能见你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.31,0:20:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 我还是无可救药的想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都很狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 明之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于不知道自己想要什么的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不可能得到那些东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有你所没有的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是12厘米的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的东西 这家伙全都得到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所拥有的东西都是我渴望得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 我就是那12厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.50,0:21:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的希洛克和憎恨产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希洛克?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 他是扎穆德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.69,0:21:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤都破了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.15,0:21:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古市…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获得一分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.49,0:21:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是一直在努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:21:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日以继夜 孜孜不倦地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我终于明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事一点意义都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果才是关键
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否被选中才是关键 不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.26,0:22:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢 现在心情好像很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.33,0:24:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于千疮百孔 成痴成狂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱是妄想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.63,0:24:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于相隔千里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.71,0:24:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过蔚蓝的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运的时刻即将到来





